油，BMW既就真係唔好搞佢。<br />\n<br />\np.s自己好多客都奶晒野之後過黎換波箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廠都有好多呢d case....日本車同歐洲車唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"*唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"thx ching 咁我唔使成日擔心要換啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信個不知名網友都唔信ZF，人地官方連oil change kit都出埋，你唔鍾意用原裝嘅買Febi都得，仲有幾間大廠都有出ZF波箱用既oil change kit，包一個油pan同起碼4L油做partial change，之後cycle gears再補足油同做adaptation reset就基本上搞掂，只係真係有好多車房連咁簡單嘅嘢都做唔嚟，或者車主根本係冇腦，揸到散哂完全郁唔到之前一刻先去換油，個波箱咁嘅情況下再換波箱油就蛇都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本常職就係所有潤滑油都會老化，你真係冇常識嘅，睇番ZF個官方guideline，直頭寫到明俾你睇d油會aging，叫你最遲一80000-120000km或八年後一定要apply一次oil change kit。 <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Depending on the driving style, ZF recommends a transmission oil change every 80,000 to 120,000 km or after eight years at the latest.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nBMW話lifetime，當然啦，佢都唔係講緊你條命，佢係講緊個波箱條命咋嘛，就係100000km囉， no magic，語言偽術。你波箱啲油夠期都唔換波箱油嘅話，咪死波箱囉，哩d就叫求仁得仁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zf.com/global/media/medien_mastersite/aftermarket/service_information/service_information_zf/transmission/cars_4/englisch_3/modelluebergreifend_1/ZF_SI_Oelwechselkit_8HP_50130_EN.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zf.com%2Fglobal%2Fmedia%2Fmedien_mastersite%2Faftermarket%2Fservice_information%2Fservice_information_zf%2Ftransmission%2Fcars_4%2Fenglisch_3%2Fmodelluebergreifend_1%2FZF_SI_Oelwechselkit_8HP_50130_EN.pdf&d=YaD4eHlGJtkOGsmHzZwWNUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ed5e78a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zf.com/global/media/medien_mastersite/aftermarket/service_information/service_information_zf/transmission/cars_4/englisch_3/modelluebergreifend_1/ZF_SI_Oelwechselkit_8HP_50130_EN.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"527b4e053df1edd0b87ec4fae432cf709d724b3b","tid":800400,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35f0e37868db4331